# Format:
# type(scope): short imperative summary
#
# Examples:
# feat(frontend): add connector status badge
# fix(api): return explicit auth error on expired session
# refactor(shared): simplify model detection helpers
#
# Types:
# feat, fix, refactor, perf, docs, test, chore, ci, migration
#
# Suggested scopes:
# api, frontend, shared, auth, db, settings, chat, build, docs, tests
#
# Rules:
# - Write in English
# - Use imperative mood
# - Keep subject <= 72 chars
# - No trailing period
# - One concern per commit
#
# What, why, validation (if applicable) and refs (if applicable)
# -
